13:00.000 --> 13:02.000
your art practice.

13:02.000 --> 13:04.000
Because the difference between saying

13:04.000 --> 13:06.000
"I do plays"

13:06.000 --> 13:08.000
and "I

13:08.000 --> 13:10.000
help solve

13:10.000 --> 13:12.000
the loneliness epidemic

13:12.000 --> 13:14.000
by connecting people powerfully

13:14.000 --> 13:16.000
in community"

13:16.000 --> 13:18.000
is how you translate

13:18.000 --> 13:20.000
your art practice to funder speak.

13:20.000 --> 13:22.000
Because funders often think

13:22.000 --> 13:24.000
very academically.

13:24.000 --> 13:26.000
And you have to do a little bit of work to just translate

13:26.000 --> 13:28.000
the work you do into

13:28.000 --> 13:30.000
what they're funding.

13:30.000 --> 13:32.000
And for me,

13:32.000 --> 13:34.000
I started

13:34.000 --> 13:36.000
my background

13:36.000 --> 13:38.000
is in music technology.

13:38.000 --> 13:40.000
So I

13:40.000 --> 13:42.000
one of my pivotal moments

13:42.000 --> 13:44.000
