13:48.000 --> 13:50.000
And the reason I

13:50.000 --> 13:52.000
did it was because

13:52.000 --> 13:54.000
me and Michael

13:54.000 --> 13:56.000
are pretty stupid. It made us laugh.

13:56.000 --> 13:58.000
To try to

13:58.000 --> 14:00.000
translate into academic

14:00.000 --> 14:02.000
language, we wanted to create

14:02.000 --> 14:04.000
a way for people to play together.

14:04.000 --> 14:06.000
We wanted creativity

14:06.000 --> 14:08.000
and music making

14:08.000 --> 14:10.000
to be a community

14:10.000 --> 14:12.000
event and a community activity.

14:12.000 --> 14:14.000
Because I can write a song

