detach when people are interacting

15:06.000 --> 15:08.000
with our installation.

15:08.000 --> 15:10.000
So then again, that has

15:10.000 --> 15:12.000
been a constant part of

15:12.000 --> 15:14.000
my original story, just humor

15:14.000 --> 15:16.000
and fun and

15:16.000 --> 15:18.000
using and recontextualizing

15:18.000 --> 15:20.000
technology, usually about

15:20.000 --> 15:22.000
tech. And if you go to the next

15:22.000 --> 15:24.000
slide.

15:26.000 --> 15:28.000
Yeah, all of this just goes out to

15:28.000 --> 15:30.000
the why it's powerful.

15:30.000 --> 15:32.000
Like, the reason that we're doing

15:32.000 --> 15:34.000
art.

15:34.000 --> 15:36.000
There's usually an underlying

15:36.000 --> 15:38.000
desire driving your work, whether it's to

15:38.000 --> 15:40.000
connect people, whether

15:40.000 --> 15:42.000
it's to connect to our communities.

15:42.000 --> 15:44.000
There's always this underlying "why" that's really

