And I think

15:50.000 --> 15:52.000
part of, as you start showing your

15:52.000 --> 15:54.000
why,

15:54.000 --> 15:56.000
and start thinking about your art

15:56.000 --> 15:58.000
in that way, it's

15:58.000 --> 16:00.000
